title: Luke Willson said new contract offer not serious! | Ian & Puck Show | Seattle's Sports Radio 950 KJR
text:
Luke Willson said new contract offer not serious! posted by Adam Loewy - 
Seahawks Tight End Luke Willson joined Ian Furness and Jason Puckett, and said the Seahawks offered him a new contract, but it wasn't extremely serious. Below is the full interview. E-Mail - Ian Furness - Jason Puckett sits in with Furness for the very long and taxing three hours, in addition, he anchors the news from 10am-3pm. You can reach Puck at and you can follow him at Twitter @jasonpuckettkjr Contact
